history.text: I did not know that Anna's voice was played by 3 actresses during the Frozen movie.
I correct myself, there were 4 voices played as Anna.
What was the plot of the Frozen movie?
I didn't know that either. I was surprised to learn that Anna, Elsa and Kristoff were voiced by multiple actors
Frozen is the story of a princess who sets off on a journey with a snowman and a reindeer to find her estranged sister

Strangely enough, it is based on a fairy
 tale called "The Snow Queen".
I wonder what other movies that Idina Menzel also acted in.
I'm not sure about that, do you agree with the critics that Frozen is a terrific family movie?
I think it does have great comedy and adventure elements to the movie and I like it.
Did you enjoy the music?
I did enjoy the musical performances. How about you?
I did find the songs very catchy and that they stayed with me throughout the day.

The story of how the sisters be
came estranged is very sad, what did you think about it?
I remember the scene where Elsa was playing with Anna and she accidentally hurt Anna and then they were separated as they grew up.
It was sad but it adds to the story.
Yes, it was very important to the story. Do you think the king and queen did the right thing by separating the girls/
Not to mention Elsa had suppressed her magic as she was growing up. The king and queen were probably trying their best interest for safety
Then, Elsa reaches 21 and then she unleashes her powers as a result of Anna's love interest.
Why do you think Elsa objected to the proposal?
I guess she didn't want to feel lonely and afraid.
That makes sense, it's too bad because she ended up alone in a palace of ice anyway
The castle Elsa built of ice was beautiful but cold.
and far away from the kingdom
I wonder what Elsa did while being alone in that ice castle.
Then Anna finds Elsa and then her heart becomes frozen
That was very exciting when Elsa froze Anna's heart
I was very surprised to learn that Hans was actually plotting against the sisters
Shocking in my opinion. Hans was setting his sights on the throne.
He was going to have both sisters killed, but one managed to escape
That is true. Anna's hair was turning white from the spell as well.
Yes, because she was freezing from the inside
the "act of true love" was supposed to break the spell

ard to break the spell
